BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 159.12 740 Td (UNDERSTANDING THE DEPRESSION CYCLE) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 700 Td (Depression creates a vicious cycle that keeps you stuck:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 682 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (  LOW MOOD --> WITHDRAWAL --> LESS ACTIVITY --> FEWER REWARDS) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 646 Td (       ^                                            |) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td (       |____________________________________________|) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 610 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 592 Td (When you feel depressed, you naturally do less. But doing less means) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 574 Td (fewer opportunities for pleasure, accomplishment, and connection.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 556 Td (This CONFIRMS depressive thoughts \('Nothing matters', 'I can't do anything'\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 538 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 520 Td (CBT for depression breaks this cycle through BEHAVIORAL ACTIVATION:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 502 Td (Instead of waiting to feel motivated, you ACT FIRST and let mood follow.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 484 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 466 Td (KEY PRINCIPLE: Action comes BEFORE motivation, not after.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 448 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 430 Td (The Depression Triangle:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 412 Td (  THOUGHTS: 'I'm worthless, nothing will help, what's the point') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 394 Td (  FEELINGS: Sad, empty, hopeless, guilty, irritable) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 376 Td (  BEHAVIORS: Isolating, sleeping too much, avoiding tasks) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 358 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 340 Td (This workbook will help you:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 322 Td (  1. Identify YOUR depression cycle) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 304 Td (  2. Schedule activities that bring pleasure and mastery) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 286 Td (  3. Challenge hopelessness and self-critical thoughts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 268 Td (  4. Build energy gradually through structured activation) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 250 Td (  5. Prevent relapse by recognizing warning signs early) Tj ET

endstream
